ZH: 我今天去商店买了一些水果。
EN: I bought some fruits at the store today.

ZH: 我们家买了新的电视。
EN: My family bought a new TV.

ZH: 昨天我买了一本好看的小说。
EN: Yesterday I bought a good novel.

ZH: 我想买一双新鞋。
EN: I want to buy a new pair of shoes.

ZH: 我明天要去市场买蔬菜。
EN: I will go to the market to buy vegetables tomorrow.

ZH: 妈妈买了一些牛奶和鸡蛋。
EN: Mom bought some milk and eggs.

ZH: 我们决定在网上买一张飞机票。
EN: We decided to buy a plane ticket online.

ZH: 我想去商场买一些衣服。
EN: I want to go to the mall to buy some clothes.

ZH: 小明买了一本中文词典。
EN: Xiaoming bought a Chinese dictionary.

ZH: 你想买什么礼物给他？
EN: What gift do you want to buy for him?

ZH: 今天我跟朋友一起买了午饭。
EN: I bought lunch with friends today.

ZH: 奶奶每周去买菜。
EN: Grandma goes shopping for groceries every week.

ZH: 我们需要买一些牙刷和牙膏。
EN: We need to buy some toothbrushes and toothpaste.

ZH: 我们打算明天去商店买一些饼干。
EN: We plan to go to the store tomorrow to buy some cookies.

ZH: 我们可以在这个超市买到所有需要的东西。
EN: We can buy everything we need at this supermarket.

ZH: 她买了一辆新车。
EN: She bought a new car.

ZH: 他买了一些漂亮的家具。
EN: He bought some beautiful furniture.

ZH: 我们下周要去买圣诞礼物。
EN: We are going to buy Christmas gifts next week.

ZH: 他买了一件漂亮的外套。
EN: He bought a nice coat.

ZH: 我打算今天晚上去买一些零食。
EN: I plan to go buy some snacks tonight.
